reviewText: Excellent Movie And All The Wonderful Movie Stars Artists In It,That We Have Lost To Time. It's Sad How Much Hollywood Has Changed For The Worst,Even The Movies And Stars Can't Behave Them Selves. Thank You To Ruth Oscar & Amazon. Com For Making My Dream Come True. To Actually Find This On Dvd,I Would Recommend This Fantastic Film To Everyone. This Will Take You Back  To The "Good Old Day's".
